text: El Potrero is a corregimiento in La Pintada District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 3,165 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 2,672; its population as of 2000 was 2,815. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
